sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as FastAPI Gateway
    participant CEO as Executive AI
    participant RC as Research Coordinator
    participant DE as Domain Expert
    participant MR as Market Research
    participant CI as Competitor Intelligence
    participant TR as Technical Research
    participant PM as Product Manager
    participant BL as Backend Lead
    participant LTM as Long-Term Memory
    participant SEM as Semantic Memory

    Client->>API: POST /projects {goal}
    API->>CEO: plan(goal)
    CEO-->>API: ceo_plan

    API->>RC: plan(goal)
    RC-->>API: research_plan (objectives per specialist)

    par Parallel research
        API->>DE: execute(goal)
        DE-->>API: DomainKnowledgeReport
    and
        API->>MR: execute(goal)
        MR-->>API: MarketResearchReport
    and
        API->>CI: execute(goal)
        CI-->>API: CompetitorMatrix
    and
        API->>TR: execute(goal)
        TR-->>API: TechnicalResearchReport
    end

    API->>RC: execute(goal, domain, market, competitor, technical)
    RC-->>API: ResearchReport (deduped, conflicts surfaced)

    API->>CEO: review_research(goal, research_report)
    CEO-->>API: APPROVE / CHANGES

    Note over API,PM: Product Manager only runs after research is merged and reviewed

    API->>PM: execute(goal, research_report)
    PM-->>API: BusinessRequirementsDocument

    API->>BL: plan_implementation(business_requirements)
    BL-->>API: tech_plan

    API->>CEO: review(goal, requirements_summary, tech_plan)
    CEO-->>API: APPROVE / CHANGES

    API->>LTM: save_project(...) + save_execution_log(...) per agent call
    API->>SEM: upsert_project(project_id, goal, research_summary)

    API-->>Client: ProjectResponse (research_report, business_requirements, tech_plan, review)
